author: Source: San Jose Mercury News
title: Concord: Man, 20, dead in shooting - San Jose Mercury News
text:
A citizen called police at 9:29 p.m. to report the sound of a gun shot in the 1100 block of Meadow Lane near the intersection of Monument Boulevard and Oak Grove Road, Concord police spokesman Corp. Chris Blakely said. Officers found a man on the ground with a single gunshot wound in an undisclosed part of the body.
 San Jose Mercury News.
